>>> Traits

T : trait _
x T == Text (format "T _" x)

x : T 'foo

show x

---

x ==> T foo

>>> Traits with patterns

A : trait _

B : trait A -- B receives the **value of** A, not the A value itself
b B == Text (format "B _" b)

b : B (A 'foo)
show b

---

b ==> B foo

>>> Passing an invalid value to a trait

A : trait _
B : trait A

B 'foo

---

Cannot use this value to represent this trait
    Calling '<trait>' (4:1)
    Importing program

>>> Conformances

A : trait _
x A == Text (format "A _" x)

B : trait _
x A == B (A x)
a B == Text (format "B _" a)

show (A 'foo)
show (B (A 'foo))

---

(A 'foo) ==> A foo
(B (A 'foo)) ==> B A foo

>>> Conformance without binding a name

A : trait _

A == Text "A"

show (A _)

---

(A _) ==> A
